## §4 — Backend RED (Rust)

The new Tauri command (`list_postgres_types`) and the trait method
(`RdbAdapter::list_types`) and the inherent method
(`PostgresAdapter::list_types`) and the SQL constant
(`LIST_TYPES_SQL`) and the unit test
